name: .WSXKEY File Extension
summary: Learn about .WSXKEY files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: To use a WSXKEY as a Winstep software license, place it in the C:/​Users/​Public/​Documents/​Winstep/​Licenses directory and double-click it. This will register your copy of your Winstep software.
